   Subscription Information

   You can sign up now for periodic updates on the status and progress of
   DisabilityDirect.gov. Announcements about the site will be delivered
   directly to you via email.

   To receive these updates, you will need to provide your email address.
   You will be sent a request to confirm you subscription, as well as
   instructions on how to take your name off this list.

   Subscribe to the list



                              Privacy Notice

   As long as you remain a subscriber to
   disabilitydirect.gov-announcement, your email address will be
   maintained by the U.S. Department of Labor (DOL) as part of its
   official record consistant with applicable records management
   regulations. We'll send you only the information you've requested; and
   we won't share your email address with anyone outside of DOL in
   accordance with the DOL Privacy and Security Statement.

   Once you subscribe, you will be sent a request to confirm your
   subscription. If you do not confirm your subscription within seven
   days, we will purge your email address.

   If you unsubscribe, we will remove your email address from the list
   within 48 hours.

   Link to www.FirstGov.gov Website Sponsored by the Office of Disability
   Employment Policy, U.S. Department of Labor

